{"type": "article", "id": 30228, "title": "为海绵设计的床", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-27T22:59:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 109, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160727225750yo5tleJHW9zUh6Iu.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>将每个碗碟刷洗干净之后，辛苦工作的海绵也到了要上床休息的时候：这个名为 Clean Dreams 的“海绵床”是双人设计组合 <a href=\"http://www.wishlist-design.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">wishlist</a> 为 <a href=\"http://www.ototodesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">OTOTO</a> 设计的一款海绵支架。这件微型家具由塑料制成，可以放进洗碗机中清洗。床架的功能与肥皂盒类似，能够储存海绵滴下的水分。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.ototodesign.com/collections/kitchen/products/copy-of-button-up-magnetic-holders\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 15 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607272258067DZ8aliAwcxObvIT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.710269\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727225806KW9A84HMlYXupQs1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727225807GVH7TCfvOZolEqkc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.691932\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727225807qXJwhaPQGF4BtZmA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}